<p>I have shared with  students and colleagues when they need this, so <strong>very handy</strong>! Share stuff and retweet whatever of interest. Retweet not necessarily endorsement, see this for example on Vatican divesting:</p>

<blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">I almost can&#39;t *believe* it but I am sharing vatican news. Apparently, &quot;da Vatican&quot; divests. The question <br />now is...where are they re-investing, what kind of impact-projects are they choosing, by which criteria? üßê <a href="https://t.co/OELQfo52fV">https://t.co/OELQfo52fV</a></p>&mdash; Massimo Pizzol (@m_outreach) <a href="https://twitter.com/m_outreach/status/1328620664341803009?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 17, 2020</a></blockquote>
