<p><strong>Topics</strong>: sustainability, climate, LCA, modelling, and ‚Äúmeta‚Äù on research, sometimes politics. NO COVID! No personal stuff (kids, dogs). Too many GIFs maybe? I am maybe a bit noisy.</p>

<p>No real <strong>strategy</strong>. This is maybe why I have no followers‚Ä¶I have no time for this really, it becomes too much. Like <a href="https://twitter.com/jacomyma">Mathieu Jacomi</a> says in the first webinar, I don‚Äôt understand what works and not works on twitter. It‚Äôs like that. What tweets get a lot of impressions and why? Who knows.</p>

